# GitHub Linguist language stats
#
# Dillrex source is the real language surface of this repo.
*.drx linguist-language=Dillrex
*.drxc linguist-language=Dillrex

# Python is the seed/runtime/tooling layer for bootstrapping, so hide it
# from the GitHub language bar.
dillrex/**/*.py linguist-vendored
tests/**/*.py linguist-vendored

# Project metadata, docs, scripts, and assets should not compete with
# Dillrex in the language stats.
*.md linguist-documentation
*.cmd linguist-vendored
*.sh linguist-vendored
*.ps1 linguist-vendored
*.vbs linguist-vendored
*.toml linguist-vendored
assets/** linguist-vendored
